trans-unit.source: Represents an event provider that routes ASP.NET tracing events to the IIS 7.0 infrastructure.
ASP.NET health monitoring enables administrators to manage deployed Web applications.
trans-unit.target: Permite que os administradores gerenciem de monitoramento de integridade ASP.NET implantado aplicativos da Web.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Management> namespace contains the event types that obtain health-status data and the provider types that process this data.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Management> namespace contém os tipos de evento que obtêm dados de status de integridade e os tipos de provedor que processam dados.

trans-unit.source: It also contains supporting types that help you manage health events.
trans-unit.target: Ele também contém suporte a tipos que ajudam você gerenciam eventos de integridade.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Management.IisTraceWebEventProvider> class is a customized health-event provider that processes ASP.NET tracing events by routing them through the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] tracing infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Management.IisTraceWebEventProvider> classe é um provedor de evento de integridade personalizado que processa eventos de rastreamento do ASP.NET, roteá-los por meio de [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] infra-estrutura de rastreamento.

trans-unit.source: This routing occurs only when tracing is enabled in ASP.NET.
trans-unit.target: Este roteamento ocorre somente quando o rastreamento está habilitado no ASP.NET.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.Management.IisTraceWebEventProvider> is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)].
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
This class does not route [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] trace events into ASP.NET page events.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não encaminhar [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] eventos da página de eventos de rastreamento em ASP.NET.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Management.IisTraceWebEventProvider" /> class.
The <xref:System.Web.Management.IisTraceWebEventProvider.%23ctor%2A> constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Management.IisTraceWebEventProvider.%23ctor%2A> construtor não se destina a ser usado diretamente no seu código.

trans-unit.source: It is called by ASP.NET.
<xref:System.Web.Management.IisTraceWebEventProvider.%23ctor%2A> is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)].
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
Moves the events from the provider's buffer into the event log.
When this method is called, all the events in the buffer are immediately moved from the buffer to the event log.
trans-unit.target: Quando este método é chamado, todos os eventos no buffer imediatamente são movidos do buffer para o log de eventos.

trans-unit.source: This occurs regardless of how much time has elapsed since the last event was written or how many events are in the buffer.
trans-unit.target: Isso ocorre independentemente de quanto tempo decorrido desde o último evento foi gravado ou quantos eventos no buffer.

trans-unit.source: The time of the last written event is reset to the time of the flushing action.
trans-unit.target: A hora do último evento gravado é redefinida para o tempo da ação de liberação.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.Management.IisTraceWebEventProvider.Flush%2A> is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)].
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
The name of the provider as specified in the configuration system.
A collection that contains the initialization values that are specified in the configuration system.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Management.IisTraceWebEventProvider" /> with the data that is necessary to process events.
<xref:System.Web.Management.IisTraceWebEventProvider.Initialize%2A> is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)].
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
The object to process.
Processes the event that was passed to the provider.
<xref:System.Web.Management.IisTraceWebEventProvider.ProcessEvent%2A> is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)].
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
Performs tasks that are associated with shutting down the provider.
The method performs tasks that enable the application to end normally.
trans-unit.target: O método realiza tarefas que permitem que o aplicativo terminar normalmente.

trans-unit.source: An example of such a task is closing resources.
trans-unit.target: Um exemplo de uma tarefa está fechando recursos.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.Management.IisTraceWebEventProvider.Shutdown%2A> is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)].
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
